1. Install Arduino IDE
2. Arduino -> Preferences -> Additional Boards Manager Urls
http://arduino.esp8266.com/stable/package_esp8266com_index.json
3. Tools ->Board-> Board Manager
  a. Install esp8266
  b. Select Board: NodeMCU 1.0 (ESP- 12E Module) 
4. Sketch -> Include Library -> Library Manager
  a. Install PubSubClient (For MQTT links)
5. Install serial driver (CH341) for MAC
  a. Select Tools->Port	
  b. Select Baud Rate: 9600
